All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CelestialObject
    Encapsulates a persistent celestial object with: name, right ascension, and declination.
    Gallery
    Encapsulates a persistent gallery object with: title, description, Href location, reference to the creating User, and reference to the {@link List<Image>}.
    GalleryAdapter
    A RecyclerView.Adapter to display a scrolling list of Galleries.
    GalleryAdapter.OnGalleryClickHelper
    An interface that handles View.OnClickListener events for Gallery items.
    GalleryRepository
    A database repository utility for persisting Galleries to the server and retrieving them.
    GalleryViewModel
    A ViewModel to hold the LiveData for the Gallery information.
    GoogleSignInService
    A database utility service for persisting GoogleSignIn data to the server and retrieving it.
    Image
    Encapsulates a persistent image object with: title, description, file metadata (original filename and MIME type), reference to the contributing User, and reference to the actual content.
    ImageAdapter
    A RecyclerView.Adapter to display a scrolling list of Images.
    ImageAdapter.OnImageClickHelper
    An interface that handles View.OnClickListener events for Image items.
    ImageDetailFragment
    A DialogFragment that displays all the basic information of an Image.
    ImageListFragment
    A Fragment that displays a scrolling list of Images.
    ImagePreviewFragment
    A Fragment that displays the basic information about an Image, such as the title and description.
    ImageRepository
    A database repository utility for persisting Images to the server and retrieving them.
    ImageViewModel
    A ViewModel to hold the LiveData for the Image information.
    LocationService
    Utility service to acquire the GPS coordinates asynchronously.
    LoginActivity
    Controls the activity for the GoogleSignIn screen.
    MainActivity
    Controls the activity for the main screen containing the scrolling list of Images.
    NorthStarSharingApplication
    North Star Sharing is a proof-of-concept group project for Deep Dive Coding through https://www.cnm.edu/.
    NorthStarSharingWebServiceProxy
    An interface used by Retrofit to dynamically construct the HTTP GET and POST requests to the web service.
    NorthStarSharingWebServiceProxy.InstanceHolder
    A helper class to create and contain a singleton instance of the NorthStarSharingWebServiceProxy.
    PermissionsFragment
    A DialogFragment that requests permissions from the user to access Android system services, such as Internet, location, camera, etc.
    PermissionsFragment.OnAcknowledgeListener
    Callback interface for returning control to controller managing permissions request flow.
    PermissionViewModel
    A ViewModel to hold the LiveData for the Android permissions information.
    SensorService
    Utility service to acquire the camera orientation asynchronously.
    SettingsFragment
    Fragment to create and manage the widgets on the Settings screen.
    UploadPropertiesFragment
    A DialogFragment to handle entering the details of a new Image and persisting it to the server.
    User
    Encapsulates a persistent user object with: latest connected date/time, and display name.
    UserRepository
    A database repository utility for persisting Users to the server and retrieving them.
